1. Start the Backend API (Terminal 1)
Open a terminal and literally just paste this whole block in at once:

bash
-----------------------------------------------------
cd ~/Dev/Websites/smartlearnwebsite
source ~/.bashrc
set -a; source .env; set +a
cd artifacts/api-server
pnpm run dev
-----------------------------------------------------

2. Start the Frontend Website (Terminal 2)
Open a second terminal window and paste this whole block in at once:

bash
-----------------------------------------------------
cd ~/Dev/Websites/smartlearnwebsite
source ~/.bashrc
cd artifacts/smart-learn
export PORT=5173
export BASE_PATH=/
pnpm run dev 
-----------------------------------------------------
